reviews.text:
New Hotel in North Point Hong Kong=- Nice View of Harbour, and having been to Hong Kong around 30 times- I would probably have given three and a half stars. Hotel has rather odd layout.. a nice fountain, and then when you go into hotel most of ground floor is taken up by shops  selling fragrances- with no one in except the sales staff.. the registration is on the second floor. Definitely not 5 star standards re staff training.. had to use computer to find direction to most famous landmarks, shuttle to central for the airport train... but surely it is not beyond the wit of man to train  staff to smile...or say have a nice day?
No central area near reception to chat with other holiday makers..
Would I go back? Actually not in this case.

Been here several times now and it's a great hotel. Most of the staff are friendly and helpful but one or two are definitely not happy to be working there. The breakfast buffet is great with loads of options. The rooms are really great and if you get a harbour view, you'll see some fantastic sunsets. Cleaning staff are so polite and couldn't be more helpful too.

Chic hotel in North Point which has a number of great restaurants attached, with a bar as well. The view from the harbour-facing rooms is great, and rooms come at an affordable price as well. The bottom flies also have a shopping mall attached. This hotel is overall a new, fairly unknown one and the value here is amazing.

Brand new hotel with good sized rooms with modern fittings plus power shower. Good service team. Love the rooftop bar. Easy access to MTR rocks (5min walk) plus there’s a fruit store and Watson’s nearby to sort out any of your needs. Definitely coming back next in Hong Kong.

Very good services and rooms are clean. Bay view is gorgeous. Hotel have settled goes to near by town centers for shopping and dinning.  Subway access is just hundred yards away.  Other public transportation s are close by.   I like this hotel and it's location.

非常推薦！離北角站蠻近的 （A1出口）
雖然房間不算大，但非常舒適且非常整潔
有很多貼心的準備
飯店有24小時健身房、無邊界泳池可以使用
入住第一天房間有提供免費的mini bar，還有膠囊咖啡機可以使用！
吹風機是大台的，對長頭髮的女生來說非常貼心
房間提供免費手機可以連上網使用，也可以免費撥打特定國家國際電話和香港本地，非常便利！！
（若開起網路共享才需要額外費用）
房間都有海景，主要是窗戶的大小、規格不同
23樓有露天酒吧可以在晚上放鬆看夜景
如果不想被送錯東西到房間,跟你說馬上來取走,但你等了半小時都不來,趁你不在才默默進房取走,不想要光是辦個入住就要等很久等到前面的人都喊要投訴了飯店還是無感,不想要要拿杯子使用卻發現遺留上一個房客的咖啡以及湯匙上有一圈乾掉的咖啡垢,不想要房間沒有清理,請不要選擇它,同樣的價位會有更好的選擇!
加價之後太貴了。
